data.description: Welcome home to this spacious 2 story, 4 bedroom 2.5 bath with separate office space or 5th bedroom!  Over 2700 sq ft of living space!  Kitchen is a delight with granite counters, kitchen island, pantry, and a gas stove. Tile floors on the entire first floor.  Two living areas AND two dining areas!  Or use one as a game room space!  So much space for those dinner gatherings!   Enjoy outdoor living on your oversized covered back patio and large back yard.  Convenient location just miles away from the heart of the Woodlands. Easy access to 99 and 45 makes your commute easy! No direct back neighbors! Just minutes from the Exxon/Mobil campus.
